Descrizione:
JEMP (Junior Enterprise of Politecnico di Milano) presents “From Contrast to Identity: Create Your Logo” a workshop where you’ll have the opportunity to design your own trademark!

Participants will dive into the fundamentals of design and visual communication, learning how to make ideas converge into a unique Brand Identity. A perfect opportunity for anyone looking to unleash their creativity and explore the process behind the creation of a brand.

See you there!

April 10, 2025 | 2:30 PM – 4:30 PM
Fabbrica del Vapore, via Giulio Cesare Procaccini 4, Milan.

